{"tid":2300810,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍屍仲繼續撐政府有咩意思？","createTime":"2020-11-25T23:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T10:56:03.000Z","uid":127575,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"cda3b7c3bf26495dda097b85c25713377d8fc946","tid":2300810,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:41:09.000Z","msg":"派錢就唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立法會只有保皇黨.....保皇黨都唔提派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明都已經冇晒反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保皇黨擺明當藍屍係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍係咪真係咁願意用安心出行App<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆淺藍都屌鳩柒婆防疫措施做到一Pat屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆仲鬧柒婆害到佢返唔到大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n柒婆防疫措施做到一Pat屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍仲有咩理由去撐政府做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍仲話台灣防疫成功係假同係造假數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連澳門同廣東省政府都唔撚信任柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍屍到底會點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857f2d2f695d6ef62e5a97bde85533613cf443c2","tid":2300810,"uid":300006,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:42:47.000Z","msg":"奴隸係咁"},{"pid":"86b8877e10439b5848c60bb3624dbec82119c6d8","tid":2300810,"uid":127575,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"明明有國安法...唔係好安全咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7e7826deb03f009a68db2d5be0f53b410fe13d","tid":2300810,"uid":340106,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:45:07.000Z","msg":"樓主應該po藍屍gp"},{"pid":"7f50cb38f74f589f90dc3cb4a62aaca25